FILE
	/usr/System/obj/user.c

NAME
	send_phrase - send a Phantasmal phrase object to the user

PROTOTYPE
	int send_phrase(object phrase)

CALLED BY
	System, Common, Game

DESCRIPTION
	Send the user the phrase in question, filtered by the state
	stack and localized to the user.

RETURN VALUE
	The number of bytes sent.

ERRORS
	Return -1 if unable to send

SEE ALSO
	message, new_simple_english_phrase, send_system_phrase
